{"tid":2167261,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"不知者嚇死，知者笑死 - 蔣芸","createTime":"2020-08-21T03:54:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T03:54:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cc1cffcd50413784cffc01f0fac5dcf44145f2f8","tid":2167261,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T03:54:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200724/Q34ZDNYQPRF7TCUGSRYNT46CRU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200724%2FQ34ZDNYQPRF7TCUGSRYNT46CRU%2F&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliuz%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=30e6cd61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200724%2FQ34ZDNYQPRF7TCUGSRYNT46CRU%2F&h=994f6d93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200724/Q34ZDNYQPRF7TCUGSRYNT46CRU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n不知者嚇死，知者笑死 - 蔣芸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DZgU8eL6lxob2_1vhfwv3jbUeH0=/570x411/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/H35QKFEMPFFEHMU3TKJL3ZTEDE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDZgU8eL6lxob2_1vhfwv3jbUeH0%3D%2F570x411%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FH35QKFEMPFFEHMU3TKJL3ZTEDE.png&h=7c5355e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唉，亭老老矣，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n許多朋友傳來傳去的那段視頻便證明上述所言不虛；。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n白痴也不能相信的事，千真萬確從他那很普通的普通話中說了出來，並不是要說給你、我、他香港人聽的，看來他有特定對象，是準備東山復出將以有為嗎？<br />\n<br />\n已有同文馮睎乾詳細分析亭老發言內容，讀之幾番大笑之餘，忍不住要把這位與在下屬蕭條同代人的大話西遊再溫；馮睎乾與亭老是隔代人，他就內容不合情理的「作文處」來批其不可信之處，我則是同代人之感慨；認識亭老時，他正紅紅火火的沉迷炒金，會算人者未必識算自身，他也曾搞餐館，可惜識人不明被夥計穿櫃底，加上生意不景，只好關門，也收過不少徒弟；後遠走他鄉師出無名無疾而終。他最津津樂道的是楊貫一的阿一鮑魚是他調教出來的，卻不知人家一早已是鮑魚痴，日思夜想的是如何推陳出新，千辛萬苦才維持盛名不衰。<br />\n<br />\n不甘寂寞說從前，其實牽強附會到不知所云，。。。。。。。。。"}]}